Columbus Bar Association v. Boggs.

[Cite as Columbus Bar Assn. v. Boggs (1988), 39 Ohio St. 3d 601.]

(No. D.D. 88-19 — Submitted September 21, 1988 — Decided October 19, 1988.)

Kenneth R. Boggs is publicly reprimanded.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Locher, Holmes, Douglas, Wright and H. Brown, JJ., concur.
